summary: AN ORDINANCE vacating a portion of Boren Avenue North lying between the south line of John Street and the north line of Denny Way and a portion of John Street lying between the east line of Boren Avenue North and the west line of Fairview Avenue North, as established in City of Seattle Condemnation Ordinance No. 51975, on the petition of the Seattle Times Company (Clerk File No. 300309).
